data.title: Duffy "Rockferry" - March 3rd (UK)
data.meta_description: Debut release from Welsh soul-singer Duffy. Albums second single "Mercy" went to #1 in the UK and I'm sure the album will follow.  http://img136.imageshack.us/img136/9966/duffyrockferryfn2.
data.text:
Post by Mikal on

Debut release from Welsh soul-singer Duffy. Albums second single "Mercy" went to #1 in the UK and I'm sure the album will follow.

Tracklisting:

1. "Rockferry" 4:14

2. "Warwick Avenue" 4:48

3. "Serious" 3:48

4. "Stepping Stone" 3:28

5. "Syrup & Honey" 3:18

6. "Hanging On Too Long" 3:56

7. "Mercy" 3:42

8. "Delayed Devotion" 2:57

9. "Scared" 3:08

10. "Distant Dreamer" 5:05

I love the album and can't wait to buy it on Monday.
